Xiao Tuo, have you ever despaired?

23
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:48,320
Yes, many times.

24
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:54,120
When I first knew I was sick,

25
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:58,540
I didn't want to accept it or tell anyone.

26
00:02:58,540 --> 00:03:05,000
So many times I tried to sleep it off and end it all.

27
00:03:06,700 --> 00:03:09,060
And then my grandpa passed away.

28
00:03:10,700 --> 00:03:14,020
I felt like my life was empty.

29
00:03:14,020 --> 00:03:16,460
So close to death,

30
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:20,180
I felt nothing is meaningful.

31
00:03:23,300 --> 00:03:26,520
At that time, I really couldn't hold on.

32
00:03:27,860 --> 00:03:30,560
I tried to commit suicide six times.

33
00:03:31,751 --> 00:03:38,059
I don't know if I was lucky or not.

34
00:03:38,059 --> 00:03:40,630
I got saved every time.

35
00:03:41,650 --> 00:03:43,800
It's just that close.

36
00:03:48,180 --> 00:03:51,260
That man saved me three times.

37
00:03:52,300 --> 00:03:57,660
Every time I woke up, I could see his face streaming with tears.

38
