Yes.

40
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:12,840
Hating him is the only way

41
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:18,420
I can stop thinking about how wonderful we were.

42
00:04:18,420 --> 00:04:21,580
So he can live a good life.

43
00:04:22,780 --> 00:04:26,660
I can't let him spend his whole life on me.

44
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:34,160
But it's hard to hate someone.

45
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:39,440
You can't even have a proper farewell.

46
