I want to get into medical school.

64
00:06:11,620 --> 00:06:14,200
It's my own decision.

65
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:18,700
I want to go to medical school to study neurology, and be a doctor in the future.

66
00:06:18,700 --> 00:06:24,140
Not just for my brother, but also for those desperate ALS patients.

67
00:06:24,140 --> 00:06:28,180
