72
00:06:59,420 --> 00:07:01,180
I support you too.

73
00:07:01,180 --> 00:07:04,020
Thank you, Mom. Thank you, Dad.

74
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:08,640
I used to be too bossy,

75
