Because our Lin family has been doctors for three generations.

78
00:07:22,220 --> 00:07:27,400
We've always been known as Dr. Lin.

79
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:31,660
So I've always had an obsession.

80
00:07:32,540 --> 00:07:39,440
I don't want the honor of our Lin family to end.

81
00:07:40,300 --> 00:07:46,660
That's why I've been pushing you guys to get in medical school,

82
00:07:46,660 --> 00:07:49,380
