84
00:08:01,020 --> 00:08:03,980
Dreams are dreams. Dad.

85
00:08:03,980 --> 00:08:08,900
Our Lin family will be doctors for four generations.

86
00:08:09,780 --> 00:08:12,400
I will be the next Dr. Lin.

87
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:18,160
Little Dr. Lin. Come on. Eat up.

88
00:08:43,220 --> 00:08:45,480
I've forgiven Xing Kai.

89
