96
00:09:24,140 --> 00:09:27,080
I really envy you.

97
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:31,760
Not just you and Xiao Que, but also Guangpu and Xindi.

98
00:09:32,620 --> 00:09:36,760
I've thought a lot these days.

99
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:41,190
Pushing away Xing Kai is not only reality,

100
00:09:42,650 --> 00:09:44,660
