I wouldn't be like this if I was half as strong as you.

102
00:09:55,880 --> 00:10:01,480
I'm not strong at all. I just trust Xiao Que.

103
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:10,200
I keep telling myself

104
00:10:11,260 --> 00:10:17,220
