105
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:21,060
Can you?

106
00:10:24,260 --> 00:10:29,760
Actually, blaming someone is just wanting him to stay.

107
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:32,900
I would blame her because I don't want her to go.

108
00:10:32,900 --> 00:10:35,740
Of course, I hope she doesn't leave.

109
00:10:37,180 --> 00:10:44,680
But I want her to be happy and carefree, living life without any burdens.

110
